<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink227-kilavi">oruvaḻit taṇantu vanta talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat talaimakaṭkut tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante told the heroine, as the hero who had come—having been “temporarily-absent-from-her-place”—[stood] behind the hedge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink227">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nāḷu</l>
<l>naṉṉutal pacappavu naṟuntōṇ ñekiḻavu</l>
<l>māṟṟalam yāmeṉa matippak kūṟi</l>
<l>nappirin tuṟaitōr maṉṟanī</l>
<l>viṭṭaṉai yōvava ruṟṟa cūḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>  O friend, </l>
        <l>alas, have you given up on the vow he made—  </l>
        <l>he who, </l>
        <l rend="space indent">speaking in a considerate way,   </l>
        <l rend="indent">since we would be unable to endure [separation] </l>
        <l rend="indent">as [our] good forehead grows pale  </l>
        <l rend="indent2">and fragrant shoulders grow emaciated— </l>
        <l>  remained separated from us? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
